data.description: Welcome to this MUST SEE private detached corner lot Gem in the heart of Brooklyn's most sought-after neighborhood in Bergen Beach. This charming house is brimming with potential, ready for its next new owner. A fully detached house that stands alone, ensuring MAXIMUM privacy from all sides. GATED PRIVATE DRIVEWAY with a spacious NEW enclosed covered carport ensuring security, storage, privacy and convenience. This home offers the best of city living, in walking distance to all major shopping, a lush park, schools and public transportation.  This hidden gem offers high ceilings, a bright spacious living room that flows into a dining area crafted for entertaining and family gatherings. The extended eat in kitchen leads to an expansive private fenced in backyard that can become your own private oasis in the city. Plenty of room for a pool, deck, garden and entertaining. 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, including a basement with its own private side door entrance- ideal for conversion into a revenue generating rental if desired. New roof, Updated windows, Boiler and Water tank.  An abundance of vintage charm and untapped potential make this property a rare find Don't miss out on a chance of owning a piece of Brooklyn. Envision the possibilities for yourself.
